{{multiple issues| {{orphan|date=August 2010}} {{Primary sources|date=May 2009}} }} {{Infobox University |name = Star Media Institute |established = 2000 |motto = ”Let Your light Shine” |image =[[File:Star Media Institute.jpg|100| Star Media Institute Logo]] |type = [[Private university|private]] |undergrad = ~40 |director = Samuel Muigai Njoroge |campus = [[Urban area|Urban]] |city = [[Nairobi]] |country = [[Kenya]] |website = [http://www.starmediainstitute.ac.ke/ www.starmediainstitute.ac.ke] }}
''The Star Media Institute'', founded in 2000, is a college in Kenya. It is a registered Mass Communication and IT training institution which is approved by City and Guilds International – UK as a training and Examination Centre. Star Media Institute is also registered by the Ministry of Education, Science and Technology in accordance with the Laws of Kenya – Education Act cap. 211.
It is located 3&nbsp;km from Nairobi City Centre.
